## Visiting Pages

```ruby
test "visiting the homepage" do
  visit root_url
  
  assert_selector "h1", text: "Welcome"
  assert_selector "nav", count: 1
  assert_link "Articles"
end

test "visiting articles index" do
  visit articles_url
  
  assert_selector "h1", text: "Articles"
  assert_selector ".article-card", count: 3
end
```

